name: Galaxy 01 - Galactic Collective
description:
Galactic Collective is a combination of my original digital paintings and AI technologies. 

I will create 50 different Galaxies in the Galactic Collective. Each Galaxy will have 50 editions. As a Galactic Collective holder you will be entitled to presale and secret drops of future Galaxy releases. 

What will make Galactic Collective rare? After, 5 days on sale all remaining editions of each drop will be sent to the burn wallet allowing for rarity to increase and secondary sales to rise.
